Package: bc-hrbl
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Hash-Routed Binary Layout — command-line driver
 CLI driver for the `.hrbl` binary format: verify, query, inspect and
 convert (JSON bootstrap). Built on top of libbc-hrbl which provides
 the zero-copy mmap reader, parallel writer and integrity checker.
 .
 The binary format is the source of truth. JSON conversion is one-way
 at read time (pretty dump) and a bootstrap path at write time.
